John Axford was placed on the family medical emergency list by the Colorado Rockies on Sunday . 
  His son Jameson was bitten twice by a rattlesnake last month in Arizona . 
  Jameson had surgery last Monday on his right foot to remove necrotic tissue . 
  The family will board an emergency medical flight on Monday to Denver for more treatment . 
  Right-handed reliever Axford will be out for at least three days . 
 